  <description>
    <p>fheroes2 is a recreation of Heroes of Might and Magic II game engine.</p>
    <p>This open source multiplatform project, written from scratch, is designed to reproduce the original game with significant improvements in the gameplay, graphics and logic (including support for high-resolution graphics, improved AI, numerous fixes and UI improvements), breathing new life into one of the most addictive turn-based strategies.</p>
